		"description": "<p>You utter a powerful word that stuns a target with 150 hit points or less. At the end of the target's turn, it makes a Constitution saving throw to end the effect. If the target has more than 150 hit points, it is instead rattled until the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Rare:&nbsp;</strong></em><strong>Maiming Power Word Stun.&nbsp; </strong>When a&nbsp;target succeeds on its saving throw, its movement&nbsp;is halved and it is either blinded or deafened (your&nbsp;choice) until the end of its next turn.</p>",
